sub_title: MoveQ - "Everyone has a mission and a desire, we keep it fun and real"
summary:
Me and my MoveQ team provide education, motor & cognitive competence building for children, physical training within the field of performance enhancement, physical rehabilitation, preventive health consulting, wellness and tools. We inspire and help you and your kids create a healthy lifestyle for wellbeing, fitness, longevity and performance.

Three dimensional (3D) functional training:
Our training is uniquely different to traditional structural training because it involves movement in 360 degrees around the joints were possible and activates a chain reaction involving muscles, tendons and fascia too. This is the key to developing full body synchronisation and to reducing potential injuries. 3D functional training provides loads of variation. Training variability is fun and creates the biggest benefits when we discuss human performance. This is widely documented in research and scientific papers. 

Education for Fitness Professionals.
Are you a (PT, Fitness Coach, Sport Coach or Health Practitioner) eager to become a MoveQ and/or Procedos licences trainer? We have designed Courses and Workshops with unique content involving a.o. techniques to restore motion, to reinforce movement, and to make your client react to real world stimuli. 

I am Ambassador and Master Trainer* for the following companies:
Procedos*, Reactive Training, Ultimateinstability, Pelvicore Solutions, Vitamin Well Benelux and Somnoblue.

MoveQ is representative and distributor for the above mentioned companies:
Procedos - Platform9, Golf Platforms, Education: PE One, PE Performance, Licenses in The Netherlands
Reactive Training - Core-Tex in The Netherlands
Ultimateinstability - Aqua Bag, Aqua Ball, Hydrovest in Sweden
Pelvicore Solutions - PelvicorePro in The Netherlands
MoveQ FitBoard - "Spooner" in the Benelux
